name: Holiday.Christmas card.Misteltoe.Wreath.Illustration.10,5cm x 14,5cm
description:
- It is one of my own illustrations with water color and pencil.

- The card is 10,5 cm x 14,5 cm, about 4" x 6" (DIN A6) printed on 300g paper. It contains also an envelope which color is almost the same as the card.

- I pack each card with care and it will be shipped in very safe package with cardboard cover and in the air cushion envelope. The shipment can be tracked via a tracking number.

- Besides the 'thank-you' note by each purchase, there's a 'Surprise!' gift for the customer who buys more than 3 cards. ;-)

- If you wish to order lots of amount from this card, please contact me via email, mail@su-pyo.com
